      "content": "Thanks for that. One thing I'm noticing is that some of my clients have different hair textures or styles—like people with very curly or coiled hair, or those who wear religious head coverings like hijabs. How should they approach the \"polished\" look you mentioned so they don't lose that sense of authority or look \"unprofessional\" to a traditional board?",
